Welcome to Pagecord! Your blog is live at <%= blog_home_url(@blog) %>. To help you get started, here are a few things you can try to personalise your site.

🎨 Pick a theme
Browse the Theme Garden for a ready-made design, then fine-tune it using Custom CSS until it's just right: <%= app_settings_theme_garden_index_url %>

✏️ Make it yours
Add a Home page, an About page, or anything other page you like. You can even embed posts and tags in pages using dynamic variables: https://help.pagecord.com/dynamic-variables-for-pages

📮 Post from where you already write
You can compose posts in the editor, or email a post to <%= @blog.delivery_email %> from <%= @user.email %>. You can even publish from Obsidian! https://help.pagecord.com/obsidian.

Log in to get started: <%= app_onboarding_url %>

🌱 Room to grow
You can use Pagecord Classic for free, forever. You have a 14-day free trial of the premium features. If you like what you see, subscribe to Pagecord Premium to connect your own domain name, and send email newsletters to your readers: <%= app_settings_subscriptions_url %>

